---
import BaseLayout from '../layouts/BaseLayout.astro';
---

<BaseLayout
  title="About"
  description="About AstroStat Academy — who we are, what we do, and how we serve the astronomical community."
>
  <div class="max-w-3xl mx-auto px-4 sm:px-6 py-16">
    <h1 class="text-4xl font-bold mb-6">About AstroStat Academy</h1>

    <div class="prose prose-invert prose-lg max-w-none prose-a:text-accent-teal">
      <p>
        AstroStat Academy is a non-profit initiative dedicated to raising statistical literacy
        across the astronomical community. We design and run intensive schools and workshops that
        bring together leading statisticians and data scientists with astronomers at all career stages.
      </p>

      <h2>What we do</h2>
      <ul>
        <li>Run week-long and two-week residential schools with hands-on Python tutorials</li>
        <li>Publish lecture recordings and course materials freely online</li>
        <li>Provide consulting support to research groups tackling complex statistical problems</li>
      </ul>

      <h2>Who we are</h2>
      <p>
        We are a volunteer-driven organisation founded by astronomers and statisticians who
        believe the field deserves better tools and training. Our faculty are drawn from
        leading research institutions worldwide.
      </p>

      <h2>Contact</h2>
      <p>
        Reach us at <a href="mailto:info@astrostat.academy">info@astrostat.academy</a>.
      </p>
    </div>
  </div>
</BaseLayout>
